{"tid":373526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港豬最愛】老鼠亂竄！　海底撈火鍋店遭踢爆衛生惡劣","createTime":"2017-08-25T05:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T12:54:06.000Z","uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b67e1fa4f7d79876ed0feda7b0f60469263dd8ea","tid":373526,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170825/1190174/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170825%2F1190174%2F&d=YkKN8ErseoKdUdwvRorTiJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=1179b45b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170825/1190174/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國知名火鍋餐廳「海底撈」全球分店超過270家，台灣也有分店。但最近有媒體踢爆，「海底撈」位於北京的兩家分店衛生情況可怕，老鼠在廚房地上亂竄、打掃用的掃帚和餐具一起清洗、用顧客使用的火鍋勺清理下水道等。<br />\n中國《法制晚報》報導，記者於今年5月初和7月底分別成功應徵上海底撈員工，進入位於北京的勁松店和太陽宮店工作，發現老鼠在廚房四處亂跑，更有老鼠爬進裝著食物的櫃子裏。在近兩個月時間，雖然店內曾請滅鼠公司清理過一次，但沒過幾天，又有老鼠出現。記者又發現員工一邊打掃，一邊洗碗，而用來打掃地面、牆壁和下水道的掃帚竟還拿來清理洗碗機和儲物櫃。員工又把打掃用的掃帚和抹布放進洗碗池內和餐具一起清洗，記者認為此舉不妥，但員工只說：「做好你自己的事情就好。」<br />\n店內的洗碗機雖然每天都會清洗，但只有清洗表面，裡面沾滿腐爛的食物殘渣，更可以用手刮下一層厚厚的油漬，散發出陣陣腐爛的惡臭。員工向記者表示：「你看那上面沾的油，又清洗不了，能把人給臭死，你爬在裡面聞，味兒可大了。」記者還發現員工用顧客吃火鍋用的漏勺，來清理堵塞下水管道的垃圾雜物。<br />\n根據中國大陸相關法規，食品生產經營應符合食品安全標準，保持場所環境整潔，並與有毒、有害場所以及其他污染源保持規定的距離。另外，第33條第2款規定，食品生產經營應有相應的消毒、盥洗、防塵、防蠅、防鼠、防蟲、洗滌等，以及處理廢水、存放垃圾和廢棄物的設備或者設施。（實習編譯莫詠儀／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"847f1e79bd53428e57db2f6fa9557a9769ec53a0","tid":373526,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/132948_af75d19e0699d0d3998db17990d35bcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F132948_af75d19e0699d0d3998db17990d35bcf.jpg&h=4dc0cba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n員工用火鍋勺挖水溝。翻攝《法制晚報》"},{"pid":"9e51d5c6ec2d46540cbe9a10fea33d88129671df","tid":373526,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/133007_d7e0e1c7d74c009646d33fa2db074eaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F133007_d7e0e1c7d74c009646d33fa2db074eaa.jpg&h=912a42f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗碗機蓄水池裡滿是油污髒垢。翻攝《法制晚報》"},{"pid":"2ac66f38b0585a2d50311949a8a7d428cd928b06","tid":373526,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:30:19.000Z","msg":"「海底撈」位於北京的兩家分店衛生情況可怕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔係香港，一下可以清咗間垃圾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c0ea5666d2fc6998411413d8bb9b73783abca8","tid":373526,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/133023_86f4d5f384b64d60e0de4483b607dffe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F133023_86f4d5f384b64d60e0de4483b607dffe.jpg&h=363913b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝《法制晚報》"},{"pid":"caf1e47ec53ed339bc9a10337ccd4bcee88da90e","tid":373526,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"好想嘔"},{"pid":"3089b118ac54d14ab8ae5c1a30bceef27cf4c798","tid":373526,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2513aa69a224a0208520bda68d63cb338e3f557d","tid":373526,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"講到好新